Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,=========OP==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:34.63,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}当我闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:39.08,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}一切都是那么令我感到惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:43.48,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}他们的身影又再度清楚浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:48.28,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}活生生出现在我的银幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:53.09,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我爱人的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:57.75,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我战斗时的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:07.08,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}全部都在我的脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:12.26,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我们一天的时间 让我们找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:16.54,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}引领到你世界的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:21.48,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我一个晚上 让你能再看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.98,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我就会相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:29.01,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:35.00,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,2000)}{\be1}回忆啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,=========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:22.03,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}没有地图 也没有罗盘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:27.07,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我们 扬帆出航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:36.61,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}并非去寻找既有的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:47.12,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}而是创造全新世界之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:57.30,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}过去的 旅途 仍记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:03.37,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}不论是哪一段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:10.71,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}都是一段很热闹的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.99,0:24:32.96,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回头望去 旅程激起的波浪浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:39.17,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}以温和的口吻 称读我的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.24,0:24:46.88,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}这么对我说着 发出灿烂光芒
